                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;One thing many people forget is that ArrayList is compact in memory which means that it&apos;s more cache friendly than LinkedList. LinkedList could be spread out all over RAM, while ArrayList is always snuggly packed together to take advantage of  spacial locality. This has important real world ramifications.&lt;/span&gt;

              &lt;div class=&quot;d-inline-flex ai-center&quot;&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;/users/6169894/aminm&quot; title=&quot;584 reputation&quot; class=&quot;comment-user&quot;&gt;AminM&lt;/a&gt;
