            &lt;/div&gt;

            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;@AminM Only the object references are compact. The objects themselves can be scattered... Until we get value types.&lt;/span&gt;

              &lt;div class=&quot;d-inline-flex ai-center&quot;&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;/users/1165724/swpalmer&quot; title=&quot;3,275 reputation&quot; class=&quot;comment-user&quot;&gt;swpalmer&lt;/a&gt;
