            &lt;/div&gt;

            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;@swpalmer certainly. However, in a LinkedList just to FIND the item you&apos;re looking for you&apos;re touring your RAM layout. Whereas with the ArrayList you can scan through it with very few cache misses.   Cache misses are a big deal for performance.&lt;/span&gt;

