            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;LinkedList&lt;/code&gt; has a much higher overhead per element (3 pointers per element). &lt;code&gt;ArrayList&lt;/code&gt; has 1 pointer per element. So even if the &lt;code&gt;ArrayList&lt;/code&gt; is only half filled, it will never have more overhead than &lt;code&gt;LinkedList&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;

